description:
Part 8 of 8. Revivals are events every Christian looks forward to, but due to the presence of evil in our world, some revivals can be fake and deceptive. As a Christian, how do you discern if a revival is counterfeit or genuine? Find out in this series with Pastor Steve Wohlberg.
